Description_lang: Coats your weapons with a Lethal Poison that lasts for $145420d. Each strike has a $h% chance of poisoning the enemy for ${$145420m1*4} Nature damage over $145420d. Subsequent poison applications will instantly deal $145419s1 Nature damage.
